726
00:47:00,795 --> 00:47:02,248
你说得没错
You're right.

727
00:47:09,402 --> 00:47:10,863
那这个呢?
And this?

728
00:47:20,019 --> 00:47:21,521
我得说
That's an excellent example,

729
00:47:21,558 --> 00:47:23,515
这是非常出色的秦朝瓷器
Ching Dynasty I should say

730
00:47:23,553 --> 00:47:27,148
大概在公元265年
circa 265 A.D.

731
00:47:28,867 --> 00:47:30,758
完全正确
Precisely.

732
00:47:36,777 --> 00:47:39,363
那这些呢?
And these?

733
00:47:39,400 --> 00:47:41,992
经典的青花瓷 对吧?
Typical of celadon would you say?

734
00:47:42,029 --> 00:47:43,361
让我看看 让我看看
Give me time, give me time.

735
00:47:43,398 --> 00:47:45,665
我会让你看的 先生
I am giving you time, sir.

736
00:47:45,703 --> 00:47:47,720
没错
Quite so.

737
00:47:47,757 --> 00:47:50,498
我想听听你对
I should also be interested in your views

738
00:47:50,535 --> 00:47:53,863
明朝洪武年间瓷器上印记的看法
on the marks of the Hung Wu.

739
00:47:53,900 --> 00:47:55,966
洪武瓷器的印记?
Marks of the Hung Wu?

740
00:47:56,629 --> 00:47:59,671
这可是个争论不休的问题
That's a vexed question.

741
00:48:00,256 --> 00:48:02,731
的确是个争论不休的问题 先生
Vexed question indeed, sir.

742
00:48:03,035 --> 00:48:05,559
真正的洪武瓷器是没有印记的
There are no marks on the genuine Hung Wu.

743
00:48:05,596 --> 00:48:07,872
真是让人难以忍受 先生
This is intolerable, sir.

744
00:48:07,909 --> 00:48:09,549
我来这里是想给你点好处的
I came here to do you a favor,

745
00:48:09,586 --> 00:48:11,905
而不是来做一个受拷问的学童
not to be examined as if I were a schoolboy.

746
00:48:11,942 --> 00:48:13,748
你是来这儿侦查
You came here to spy.

747
00:48:13,785 --> 00:48:15,151
不是的
Not so.

748
00:48:15,188 --> 00:48:16,577
也许你觉得
You may have found it easy

749
00:48:16,613 --> 00:48:18,348
撒个谎 伪装个身份
to inveigle your way in here

750
00:48:18,385 --> 00:48:20,251
进入我的屋子很容易
upon false pretenses

751
00:48:20,288 --> 00:48:22,262
但是我发誓 先生
but by god sir,

752
00:48:22,299 --> 00:48:26,182
你会发现从这儿出去很难
you shall find it harder to get out.

753
00:48:26,219 --> 00:48:30,856
把你的手举过头顶 华生医生
Raise your hands above your head, Dr. Watson.

754
00:48:33,111 --> 00:48:34,367
怎么回事?
What's that?

755
00:48:36,177 --> 00:48:38,798
福尔摩斯 你!
Holmes, you.

756
00:48:38,835 --> 00:48:40,609
不许动
Don't move.

757
00:48:43,213 --> 00:48:46,159
我会射穿你的脑袋
I shall shoot you through the head

758
00:48:46,857 --> 00:48:48,724
而不是心脏
rather than the heart

759
00:48:50,129 --> 00:48:52,195
然后我会告知警方
and inform the police

760
00:48:52,996 --> 00:48:55,558
说我把你误认成盗贼了
I mistook you for a common burglar.

761
00:48:55,595 --> 00:48:57,805
我以前也扮过小偷
That is a role that I've played before

762
00:48:58,400 --> 00:49:00,223
而且还成功了
with some success.

763
00:49:00,260 --> 00:49:02,242
毫无疑问 先生
Without any doubt, sir,

764
00:49:02,279 --> 00:49:05,557
这是你最后一次演出了
this will be your last time.

765
00:49:05,594 --> 00:49:07,188
-Baron! -Kitty!
-Baron! -Kitty!

766
00:49:10,949 --> 00:49:14,839
恶有恶报
Be done by your debt.

767
00:49:14,876 --> 00:49:20,122
医生 医生 救我 救我
Doctor, doctor, help me, help me.

768
00:49:20,160 --> 00:49:22,363
打电话给Baron的医生
Telephone the Baron's physician

769
00:49:50,527 --> 00:49:51,365
啊 James爵士
Ah, Sir James,

770
00:49:51,402 --> 00:49:53,335
请原谅我这么晚来打扰
forgive me for summoning you at this late hour

771
00:49:53,372 --> 00:49:58,107
但是事情紧急 你必须在苏格兰场 掺和进来之前 得到这个
but there's no time to be lost. You must have this before Scotland Yard bumbles in.

772
00:49:58,144 --> 00:49:59,141
苏格兰场?
Scotland Yard?

773
00:49:59,178 --> 00:50:03,331
Baron Gruner要指控我们 指控华生冒名顶替
Baron Gruner's laid a complaint against us, Watson as an impostor,

774
00:50:03,369 --> 00:50:04,273
而我则是入室盗窃
myself as a burglar,

775
00:50:04,310 --> 00:50:05,101
我们两个都是
we were both.

776
00:50:05,138 --> 00:50:06,644
我转移了Gruner的注意力
I diverted Gruner's attention

777
00:50:06,680 --> 00:50:09,900
而福尔摩斯则找到了那个
while Holmes procured that.

778
00:50:09,938 --> 00:50:11,670
你必须把这个拿给Merville小姐看
You must show it to Ms. Merville,

779
00:50:11,707 --> 00:50:14,524
她会发现自己只是上百个女人之一
she will find herself one among a hundred.

780
00:50:14,561 --> 00:50:16,812
Baron Gruner跟他的女受害人之间
The account of what sports

781
00:50:16,849 --> 00:50:19,967
所玩的游戏的记录
Baron Gruner enjoyed with his female victims

782
00:50:20,004 --> 00:50:22,029
也许最终可以
may have perhaps at last

783
00:50:22,066 --> 00:50:23,422
让Merville小姐睁开眼睛
open Ms. Merville's eyes.

784
00:50:23,459 --> 00:50:26,245
你真是干得太妙了 福尔摩斯先生 太妙了
You've done wonders, Holmes, wonders.

785
00:50:26,283 --> 00:50:29,076
除了Kitty Winter
Except for Kitty Winter.

786
00:50:29,113 --> 00:50:31,582
华生解释吧 我得休息了
Watson explain, I must rest.

787
00:50:31,619 --> 00:50:34,382
Winter小姐是Gruner以前的一个情妇
Ms. Winter is a former mistress of Gruner's,

788
00:50:34,419 --> 00:50:35,475
她跟踪我到了Kingston
she followed me to Kingston,

789
00:50:35,512 --> 00:50:37,981
身上藏了一瓶硫酸
concealed about her was a flask of vitriol.

790
00:50:38,018 --> 00:50:39,655
她把硫酸都泼到Gruner身上了
Which she unleashed upon Gruner.

791
00:50:39,692 --> 00:50:42,085
他的右手严重受伤
Severely damaging his right hand

792
00:50:42,121 --> 00:50:44,862
还有他的脸
and parts of his face.

793
00:50:44,900 --> 00:50:46,565
他将终身毁容
He will be disfigured for life.

794
00:50:47,567 --> 00:50:49,680
但是如果这些伤
But surely if these injuries

795
00:50:49,717 --> 00:50:51,890
像你描述的那么可怕
are as terrible as you described them

796
00:50:51,928 --> 00:50:54,307
那我们的目的就达到了啊...
then our purpose is sufficiently gained...

797
00:50:54,344 --> 00:50:56,151
她会更爱他
She'd love him the more

798
00:50:56,188 --> 00:50:58,638
把他当成一个毁了容的殉道者
as a disfigured martyr.

799
00:50:59,296 --> 00:51:03,511
我们应该毁掉的 是他的道德形象而不是他的容貌
It is his moral side not his physical which we have to destroy.

800
00:51:03,548 --> 00:51:05,538
那个本子将会让她彻底清醒
That book will bring her down to earth

801
00:51:05,575 --> 00:51:06,975
我想没有别的能做到这一点
and I knew nothing else that could.

802
00:51:07,012 --> 00:51:08,610
都是他亲手写的
It's in his own handwriting,

803
00:51:08,647 --> 00:51:10,272
她肯定认得出来
she cannot get past it.

804
00:51:10,986 --> 00:51:14,077
福尔摩斯 我和我的委托人对您感激不尽
Neither my client nor myself can thank you enough, Holmes.

805
00:51:14,894 --> 00:51:16,940
要是Winter小姐甚至是你本人
Should either Ms. Winter or even you yourself

806
00:51:16,977 --> 00:51:18,334
被警方为难
be incommoded by the police

807
00:51:18,371 --> 00:51:20,979
请马上打电话给我
do not hesitate to telephone me.

808
00:51:21,016 --> 00:51:22,379
谢谢 James爵士
Thank you, Sir James,

809
00:51:22,416 --> 00:51:23,097
不过说实在的
but to tell the truth,

810
00:51:23,134 --> 00:51:27,021
我从未受到苏格兰场的骚扰
I rarely if ever find myself inconvenienced by Scotland Yard.

811
00:51:28,905 --> 00:51:29,915
晚安
Good night.

812
00:51:29,952 --> 00:51:31,811
晚安
Good night.

813
00:51:37,007 --> 00:51:38,531
我得谢谢你 华生
I would like to thank you too, Watson.

814
00:51:38,568 --> 00:51:40,027
谢谢 James爵士
Thank you, Sir James.

815
00:51:40,064 --> 00:51:42,037
噢 还有这个
Oh, by the way,

816
00:51:44,086 --> 00:51:45,299
明朝的碗
Ming dish

817
00:51:45,337 --> 00:51:47,371
对
by jove yes.

818
00:51:47,407 --> 00:51:49,118
价值连城 我想
Worth a king's ransom I understand.

819
00:51:57,709 --> 00:51:58,851
(英国皇室徽章)
***

820
00:52:12,687 --> 00:52:13,882
福尔摩斯
Holmes.

821
00:52:15,747 --> 00:52:18,647
福尔摩斯 我发现我们委托人的身份了
Holmes, I've discovered the identity of our client.

822
00:52:18,684 --> 00:52:19,492
原来就是...
It's none other than the...

823
00:52:19,530 --> 00:52:21,447
一位忠诚的朋友和一位古道热肠的绅士
A loyal friend and a chivalrous gentleman,

824
00:52:21,483 --> 00:52:22,812
不管是现在还是将来
let that now and forever

825
00:52:22,850 --> 00:52:25,192
我们知道这一点就够了
be enough for us.

